---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import CtaBand from '../components/CtaBand.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Trucker Copilot and FactorEvo | From the Cab to Capital"
  description="See how Trucker Copilot captures load activity while FactorEvo powers the transportation finance workflow behind funding, servicing, and collections."
>
  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom:2.5rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">The FactorEvo Connection</span>
      <h1>One ecosystem from the cab to the funding decision.</h1>
      <p class="lead" style="color:var(--text-muted); max-width:44em;">
        Trucker Copilot and FactorEvo solve different parts of the same problem. Trucker Copilot
        gives drivers and carriers a practical way to capture and follow the transaction. FactorEvo
        gives participating specialty finance companies the infrastructure to evaluate evidence,
        make funding decisions, service receivables, and manage the financial relationship.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top:1rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">🚛</div>
          <h3>Trucker Copilot owns the front line</h3>
          <p>Drivers, dispatchers, and carriers use Trucker Copilot to capture load events, submit documents, communicate, and follow status.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">🏦</div>
          <h3>FactorEvo powers the financial workflow</h3>
          <p>Participating finance companies use FactorEvo to receive transactions, read and classify documents, evaluate risk, verify information, manage funding, service receivables, communicate, reconcile activity, and support collections.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">📡</div>
          <h3>Signals connect the two</h3>
          <p>The activity captured through Trucker Copilot becomes structured evidence within FactorEvo. That connection reduces reentry, protects context, and gives authorized participants one record from the road to the financial decision.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-band mt-2" style="padding:2.4rem 2rem;">
        <p style="font-size:1.35rem; font-weight:800; color:#fff; margin:0;">
          Trucker Copilot lives in the cab. FactorEvo powers the rails.<br />Signals tell the system what is true.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand
    headline="From the cab to capital."
    primaryLabel="Get Trucker Copilot"
    primaryHref="/download"
    secondaryLabel="Explore Signals"
    secondaryHref="/signals"
  />
</Base>
